        "Description": "Open Contract: Energy CEO&apos;S. These 5 CEO&apos;s have been lobbying, using propaganda, and other unorthodox means to manipulate the public into.. lets say, believing that they are the &apos;good guys&apos;. In reality, however? These 5 are all the contributing factors to global climate change. This is unacceptable, as the public buy into this. To any hitmen reading this, you know the truth now, and so do I. These 5 all are changing the world in secret, and this is your chance to end it.\r\rGodspeed.\r\r-(redacted)",
